@node Overview
@chapter Overview

@samp{use-package-extras.el} provides helper macros and a utility function that simplify Emacs configuration when using the @samp{use-package} macro. In configurations where package installation is handled by an external manager such as @samp{elpaca}, you often want @samp{use-package} declarations to configure packages without attempting to install them. This package provides a dedicated macro for that pattern, along with a shorthand for interactive lambdas and a startup-time reporter.

The package depends on @samp{use-package}.

